he\nbattle had ended I ventured to where this being stood but it had long been\ngone.  All that remained in its spot was a small circle drawn into the\nground where it had stood.<1>\n'),(8447,'table','<o>The table is decently large and made of wood.<1>\n'),(8448,'bed','<o>The large bed takes up much of the rooms interior. Its elven\ncraftsmanship is second to none. Piles upon piles of warm furs have been\nplaced here used as a mattress.<1>\n'),(8500,'grass clump','<o>This grass looks quite tasty, if you are into grass that is.<1>\n'),(8501,'flesh scrap meat','<o>This particular hunk of meat looks somewhat edible still.<1>\n'),(8502,'flesh scrap meat','<o>Brushing aside the maggots that have taken residence in this hunk of\nmeat, you decide that it might not be wise to consume this flesh.<1>\n'),(8504,'ivory tusk','<o>This tusk of purest ivory looks quite captivating to the eye.<1>\n'),(8505,'horn rhino','<o>This rhinoceros horn looks valuable in a way, or at least valuable to\nsomeone in this world.<1>\n'),(8507,'boot yellow','<o>This is a HUGE frigging<1> <y>yellow boot<o>. In another day and\nage, they might be referred to as ass-kickers.  The boot seems \nrather worn and has a small hole at the toe.<1>\n'),(35460,'coal lump','A lump of coal.  Has someone been naughty?\n'),(8513,'small dart','<o>A small dart made of wood. Its tip a point that could be used in\nkilling some creature.<1>\n'),(8514,'ball sphere ebony ebony','<o>This strange sphere is about head-sized and has three holes in its\nface.<1>\n'),(8515,'goblet','<o>This ornate cup looks quite stunning and is probably worth a\nfortune.<1>\n'),(8516,'dish','<o>This oversized plate looks quite expensive.<1>\n'),(8517,'disc ruby red portal','<o>It looks large enough to climb through.  Maybe you could enter\nit...?<1>\n'),(8518,'grass bad clump','<o>Hrm....this grass doesn\'t look too good.....<1>\n'),(8522,'boot yellow','<o>This is a HUGE frigging<1> <y>yellow boot<o>. In another day and\nage, they might be referred to as ass-kickers.<1>\n'),(8604,'tree acacia tall','<o>This tall tree stretches high above all the other trees in the area.\nIts branches are covered with leaves, food for the local giraffe\npopulation.  The tree itself is home to numerous birds and monkeys.<1>\n'),(8700,'halo fire','<o>The halo floats quietly a few inches above the ground, or over a\nwearer\'s head if it is placed there.  The flames that form it cause soft\nlight to be cast nearby.  It generates very little heat despite the\nsubstance it is made of.<1>\n'),(8701,'facemask mask blue dragonscale scale','<o>The supple dragonscale mask wraps around a wearer\'s head, and the only\nopenings are for the eyes, nose, and mouth.  Over the orifice for the\nmouth are some thin, vertical metal bars.<1>\n'),(8702,'marble fountain','This is a beautifully carved fountain depicting a natural scene.  Water flows\nfrom a large, central carved tree.\n'),(8703,'claymore runed sword','<o>The large claymore has a serrated blade and red serpentine runes twist\ntheir way along the long blade.  The handle is wrapped in brick red\nleather, and a ruby is set in the counterbalance on the end of the\npommel.<1>\n'),(8704,'suit blue dragonscale','<o>The armor covers the wearer\'s body from the shoulders down to the\nthighs. It is composed of soft, supple dragonscale, and seems to\nbe quite durable.<1>\n'),(8705,'legging blue dragonscale','<o>This is a tough legging composed of a stiff metal plate covered in\nblue dragonscales.  It fits snugly on a wearer\'s leg and will not\nhinder movement in battle.<1>\n'),(8706,'sleeve blue dragonscale','<o>The sleeve is made of a tough metal plate covered in blue dragonscales\nand looks quite durable.  It fits snugly so as to not hinder the\nwearer in battle.<1>\n'),(8707,'cloak white blue','<o>The cloak is woven of a sturdy textile and woven with blue\ndragonscales. A silver clasp holds it around the wearer\'s neck.  It seems\nto be quite sturdy and good protection against weapons and the cold.<1>\n'),(8708,'battle-armor suit dwarven armor','<o>The armor is a sturdy, dangerous looking construction.  The shoulders\nhave sharp spikes protruding from them, and all the edges are bold\nand frightening.  It is built for the bravest, scariest warriors in\nthe realms.<1>\n'),(8709,'battle-helmet dwarven helmet','<o>The helmet is made of sturdy metal and covers the wearer\'s entire\nhead. It has several spikes jutting off of it at odd angles, and is rather\nterrifying to behold.<1>\n'),(8710,'battle-boot boot dwarven','<o>This is a spiked metal boot with a hard black sole.  It is extremely\nsturdy and a fearsome piece of armor.<1>\n'),(8711,'battle-gauntlet gauntlet dwarven','<o>This gauntlet is made of a solid metal and has several sick looking\nspikes jutting off it.  It seems extremely dangerous on an angry\nopponent.<1>\n'),(8712,'battle-cape cape red chaotic','<o>The cape is a shifting color-scape of red and black, and it is almost\nhypnotic to stare at for more than a few moments.  It has a sturdy\nmetal clasp with some dangerous spikes jutting off of it.<1>\n'),(8713,'broadsword sword frosty','<o>The sword looks oddly shiny and transparent.  Upon closer inspection\nyou determine that it is made completely of ice!  It must be held together\nby a powerful<1> <p>magic<o>.<1>\n'),(8714,'boot red soft','<o>The boot is crafted from soft leather stained a deep blood red.  It has\ntough black soles that should last some time.  It is made to human size.<1>\n'),(8715,'cloak red mass material','<o>The cloak is made of a red cloth and has spidery silver runes\nembroidered along the edges.  It has a silver chain to hold it around a\nwearer\'s neck.<1>\nTo ward off the sun or cold, it has a deep hood.\n'),(8716,'ring silver red jewel','<o>The ring is made of sterling silver, and a small red ruby is set into\nit.  Along the band of the ring you can see small engraved runes.  The\nruby is held in place by what looks like several small clawed fingers,\ncarefully 