nt amount of protection for its\nwearer.  The quiver while smaller then most at least allows quick\naccess to one\'s arrows.\n'),(8725,'white cape','The cape is made of a flexible yet sturdy white material, and has a\nclasp made of pure silver.\n'),(8726,'shield metal white','The shield is crafted from a<W> bright white metal<z>, and it gleams brightly\nin even the dimmest light.\n'),(8727,'ring white metal','It is a simple band made of a <W>bright white metal<z>.\n'),(8728,'boot white metal','The boot is made of sturdy white metal plates, and it shines brightly.\n'),(8729,'shinguard white metal','The shinguard is constructed of a tough white metal plate with strong\nleather straps on the back.\n'),(8730,'vambrace white metal','This wrist guard is made of a sturdy white metal, and is crafted into\none contiguous piece for maximum durability.\n'),(8731,'white metal girth','The girth is made from a sturdy white metal that gleams brilliantly\nin even the dimmest light.\n'),(8732,'white metal gauntlet','The gauntlet is quite sturdy and is crafted from a bright white metal.\n'),(8733,'white metal spaulder','This piece of armor is designed to cover the upper arm and shoulder.  It\nis crafted from sturdy white metal, and it shines in even dim light.\n'),(8734,'white metal breastplate','The breastplate is crafted from a strong white metal, and a pale\nblue etching is a lotus flower graces the center.\n'),(8735,'white metal gorget','This piece of neck armor is made from a bright white metal and seems\nquite sturdy.\n'),(8736,'spangenhelm helmet white metal','The helm is delicately crafted yet tough.  The white metal that\ncomposes it is quite bright.\n'),(8746,'sculpture ice lotus','<o>The sculpture has been carefully chiseled from ice.  It does not seem\nto melt, despite the fact that there is water running from the fountain\nthat supports it.  A soft blue glow comes from inside of it, which\nenhances the eerily beautiful fountain and the lapis tiles of the\nplaza.<1>\n'),(