ost respected\nof mages.<z>\n'),(9737,'brooch charming','<P>It is made of some runic, magical material.<1>\n'),(9738,'robe mysterious','<P>It is made of some magical fabric and completely covered in rubies and\nemeralds that form mysterious patterns.<1>\n'),(9739,'headdress mysterious','<P>It is made of some magical fabric and completely covered in rubies and\nemeralds that form mysterious patterns.<1>\n'),(9741,'mask judgment obsidian','<r>The sheer hideous features of the mask are enough to make you look\naway, but the blood and gore splattered all over it really makes your\nstomach churn.<1>\n'),(9742,'whip intimidation','It is made of some <k>dark leather<1>, maybe some orc hide, and has small\nbits of <k>obsidian<1> at its tip.  It is badly splattered with <r>blood\nand gore<1>.\n'),(9743,'vest thievery','<k>It seems to be made of some tough leather.<1>\n'),(9744,'boot sneaking','<k>It seems to be made of some tough leather.<1>\n'),(9745,'amulet silent','It seems to be made of some <o>tough leather<1>, and has a small charm on\nit.\n'),(9746,'glove thievery','<k>It seems to be made of some tough leather.<1>\n'),(9747,'opal huge','<o>It gleams with a soft light.<1>\n'),(9748,'key master-key','<k>It is a small, diamond-studded key.<1>\n'),(9749,'rusty iron key','<o>This key looks to be as ancient as the castle itself.<1>\n'),(9752,'emerald holy symbol','<g>Emeralds are encrusted all over this ancient symbol.<1>\n'),(9753,'glove shadowy','<o>It seems to be made of some dark material that make it blend in with\nthe shadows around it.<1>\n'),(9754,'bracer shadowy','<o>It seems to be made of some dark material that make it blend in with\nthe shadows around it.<1>\n'),(9758,'axe mighty','<o>It seems to have been unused for ages as rust has eaten away most of\nits structural integrity.  It is clear from its magnificent size and from\nthe fact that it has survived the ravages of time, that it must have been\nthe mightiest weapon of its time.  Now, however, you wonder if