ckets attached to a large chain\nforces the wheels to spin in turn forcing the water to pump through the\nmachine itself.  Wire filters can be seen but there\'s no way to tell\nwhat\'s inside of it.<z>\n'),(12207,'Pearl necklace','<o>A strand of quality pearls usually worn to social functions at\nthe palace has been tempered by a mage. It sheds off an eerie glow.\n'),(12208,'glove pearl','<o>This glove is laced with pearls that line all around the\noutside of it.  It makes an excellent blocking element when\ndealing with a dull or razor sharpened weapons.  Striking an\nopponent with this glove could be lethal.\n'),(12209,'pearl belt','<o>A pelted belt of quality pearls is a perfect object to\nbe worn to either a ball or social functions held at the\npalace.  It also makes a perfect defense against slash type\nweapons.\n'),(12210,'vest pearl','<o>A pearl studded vest looks impressive. Elegant wear, light and fancy.<1>\n'),(12211,'ring pearl','Carved from pearls the ring would suit you well.\n'),(12212,'ring  glass','The ring is made from glass and looks like it can break easily.\n'),(12214,'shirt wool','A small wool shirt looks rugged and warm.\n'),(12215,'vest','A large wool vest looks rugged and warm.\n'),(12216,'suit','A light suit made from a silver metal has been designed to fit\nlarge warrior type men.\n'),(12217,'dagger','<o>A small thin brass dagger is a light weapon in your hand.  It\nhas a pointed tip but the blades edge seems dull.\n'),(12219,'gem','<k>The gemstone looks dull and grey.<1>\n'),(12220,'gem','<b>The gemstone is clear and sparkles brightly in your eyes.<1>\n'),(12221,'coat','<o>The fur coat is made up of wolf skin.  It looks very warm.<1>\n'),(12222,'charm','<p>The charm is a tiny hollow round ball attached to a thin strap of\nleather. It jingles in the palm of your hand when you move it.\n'),(12223,'warrior ring','<y>The ring is a thick piece of metal which holds a tiny yellow\ngemstone. There\'s a small inscription on it.<1>\n'),(12223,'inscription','<p>The words \"warrior ring\" has been etched on the metal.<1>\n'),(12224,'ring warrior','<k>The ring is a thick piece of metal which holds a tiny grey\ngemstone. There\'s a small inscription on it.<1>\n'),(12224,'inscription','<p>The words \"warrior ring\" has been etched on the metal.<1>\n'),(12225,'ring warrior','<b>The ring is a thick piece of metal which holds a tiny blue\ngemstone. There\'s a small inscription on it.\n'),(12226,'spinning wheel','<o>This device if not known to you is used to spin fabric made\nfor clothing.<1>\n'),(12227,'stick','<o>Scrawled on the stick are the words \"Whuppin Stick\".<1>\n'),(12351,'portal dragon','<p>A portal looks to be stable here.<1>\n'),(12401,'band coral silver ring','You see an intricate band of silver set with a <B>bright piece of\nblue coral<1>.  Its appears to have been made by a master craftsman.\n'),(12402,'runes breastplate mithril scenes battle','<c>Made of pure the mithril the breastplate is slightly\ntarnished but otherwise in perfect condition.  Etched\non its surface are glorious battle scenes.<1>\n'),(12403,'scale dragon red','You see a large scale taken from the body of a <R>red\ndragon.<1>  It has been polished nicely and has leather straps\nattached to it so that it can be worn as a breastplate.\n'),(12404,'shield serpent scale','<b>Made from the scale of a sea serpent the scale is a\noily blackish-blue in color.<1>\n'),(12405,'platinum band head','<d>You see a simple band made of pure platinum.  You can\nfind no inscriptions or carvings anywhere on its surface.<1>\n'),(12406,'key carved silver','You see a small key carved from a block of pure silver.\n'),(12407,'dress black shimmering','<k>You see an exceptionally beautiful dress made of a\nblack shimmering material.  It seems to shout at\nyou, \"Wear Me!\".<1>\n'),(12408,'ring black metal','<k>You see a simple band made of some unknown black\nmetal. It is extremely heavy for its size and cannot\nmarked in any way.<1>\n'),(31480,'rack logs fire