reat white shark.<1>\n'),(12438,'flipper shark skin','You see a <k>flipper<1> made from the hide of a great white shark.\n'),(12439,'cape shark skin','You see a large <k>cape<1> made from the hide of a great white shark.\n'),(12440,'wreath seaweed','Made of <g>thick strands of green seaweed<1> the wreath is\nscratchy and itchy to the touch.\n'),(12441,'bracelet seaweed','Made of <g>thick strands of the green seaweed<1> the bracelet\nis itchy and scratchy to touch.\n'),(12442,'club whale bone','Given that you are unfamiliar with the whale anatomy\nit is hard to say exactly what kind of bone you see.\nBut judging by its size you can definitely say that\nit is a whale bone.\n'),(12443,'jellyfish stinger whip','<B>The whip has been made from a dried and hardened\nstinger of a jellyfish.  You notice that the tip\nof the whip has an odd taste to it which makes you\nfeel light headed.<1>\n'),(12444,'shell starfish','<o>You see a bright orange shell from a starfish.\nIt has five sharp tips to it.<1>\n'),(12445,'seaweed clump','The seaweed is bland and utterly tasteless.\n'),(12446,'algae green','<g>The algae is slimy and tasteless as you try a small\npiece of it.<1>\n'),(12447,'algae black','<k>As you try a small piece of the black algae you\nnotice that it has a particular sharp taste to\nit and feels very slimy as it slides down the\nback of your throat.<1>\n'),(12449,'tail eel','<g>The tail of the eel has been dried and stiffened to make\na small rod shaped object.<1>\n'),(12450,'shell turtle large breastplate','<g>Made from a large sea turtle the shell has been outfitted\nwith leather straps to act as a breastplate.<1>\n'),(12451,'shell conch large','You see a large <R>red<1>/<o>orange<1> conch shell.\n'),(12453,'planks raft','<o>Old and worn the planks appear to be the scraps of\na shipwrecked boat that someone strapped together\nto make a raft out of.  Off to one corner of the small\nraft you find some dried bones, a blood stain, and\ntiny scratch marks depicting days