ee, you may\nenjoy the use of our stables to the west.  If you should decide to stay\nthe night, please see our receptionist just inside.\n<1>\n'),(18661,'bench weathered','<o>Constant exposure to the elements of the outdoors has weathered this bench\nquite a bit, but it is still quite sturdy.<1>\n'),(18662,'bench well worn','<o>Constant exposure to the elements of the outdoors has weathered this bench\nquite a bit, but it is still quite sturdy.<1>\n'),(18664,'hay pile','<y>It looks a bit stale, but would be suitable for a nap.<1>\n'),(18665,'bags feed stack','<o>Several differents types of feed are stored in these bags to accomodate\na variety of mounts.  They have been stacked haphazardly against the wall.\n'),(10612,'sword broad wide','Bright, sharp and deadly are words that come to mind when you examine this\nwicked sword.  The flared pommel perfectly balances against the weight of its\n<r>razor sharp<1> blade.  The hilt is made of <y>gold<1> with an <g>emerald<1> placed\nin its end.  This <g>emerald<1> glows with power anytime battle ensues.\n'),(10613,'robes ancient','Pure <w>white<1> laced fabric with <y>golden threads<1> and <w>silver<1> designs\ngive the wearer a sense of royalty and regality.  This beautifully crafted robe\nbathes in a <w>pale white<1> light thats seems to generate within itself.  There\nis little doubt that this robe was meant for a being of higher stature than\nyourself.\n'),(18668,'moosehead head','<o>This moosehead is HUGE and has an impressive rack of antlers.  It appears\nto be staring at you as you move about the room.<1>\n'),(18669,'couch plush','<p>This couch has big fluffy cushions for maximum comfort.<1>\n'),(18670,'couch black leather','<k>This couch has big fluffy cushions for maximum comfort.<1>\n'),(18671,'table coffee inlaid','<o>Intricate inlaid wood designs on the top of this table give it an impressive\nlook, both beautiful and elegant.<1>\n'),(18672,'painting battle','<W>A group of frontier guards in platemail oppose a 