cle in the middle of the room, these slabs of stone are\namazingly comfortable.<z>\n'),(34778,'bladder whale small','<B>Plucked from the finest of whales, this bladder was made for your drinking\npleasure!<z>\n'),(34779,'mask faerie face','Neatly stitched together, this mask resembles the <W>face of a delicate\nfaerie.<z>  Made from dozens of skins, the ogre who made this is certifiable.\n'),(34780,'wing pixie skin','<P>Strangely enough, if you pull enough skin from enough pixies, stitch them\njust right and add some magical dust, you can make some pretty impressive\nogre-sized wings!  The maker and wearer of these wings needs a head check!<z>\n'),(34781,'piranha skin large','<y>This poor unfortunate fish had its insides removed so that you could fill it\nwith your favorite liquid!  This waterskin still has it\'s teeth, so watch your\nlips!<z>\n'),(34782,'leopard waterskin','<y>Carefully skinned and dried, this leopard-skin waterskin can only be\ndescribed as fashionable and classy!<z>\n'),(34783,'beard fuzzy','<o>Quite the fashionable piece of armor!  Pieces of animal fur have been\ncarefully crafted onto a small piece of granite, providing style and protection.\nYou can hardly tell it\'s fake!<z>\n'),(34784,'waterskin hairy wrinkly leather skin','<r>What is there to say?  It\'s big, hairy and thirst quenching.  Upon examining\ncloser, this waterskin resembles the private parts of a cyclops.  GROSS.<z>\n'),(34785,'waterskin batwing','<k>This waterskin, made from the finest batwings, is a bit more hairy than you\'d\nexpect.<z>\n'),(34786,'gem mystifying','<G>Where this gem comes from, no one knows.  It gives the user greater power.<z>\n'),(34787,'bag large boho','This large boho bag is made from the finest material known to man, hemp.  It\'s\na classic, must have bag for anyone who deeply cares about The World.\n'),(34788,'skull huge','<w>Somewhere something is missing it\'s head.  This skull has been hollowed\nout and fashioned with a metal handle.<z>\n'),(34789,'c